commit.message:
HZN-1285: Initial Karaf assembly for Sentinel (#1938)

* HZN-1285: move extender and svc to the container project

* HZN-1285: move karaf extensions feature to container/

* HZN-1285: create common sentinel/minion container

* create a "shared" Karaf container in container/shared/
* modify the minion container to extend the shared container
* create a sentinel container that extends the shared container
* create a sentinel repository project that mimics the minion one

* HZN-1285: make a basic sentinel assembly

* HZN-1285: refactor features/*/container/karaf/ into features/container/*/

* HZN-1285: skip "default" repository and unpack repo directly into system/

* HZN-1285: update default ports to avoid conflict with OpenNMS/Minion
HZN-1288: run as sentinel rather than root; do not require jicmp

Merge pull request #1946 from OpenNMS/jira/HZN-1288
